            <commentid>25973</commentid>
            <who name="Daniel Wagner">daniel.wagner</who>
            <bug_when>2011-07-12 16:56:58 +0200</bug_when>
            <thetext>Using the &quot;Toggle Displayed Sets&quot; feature causes the application&#39;s data model to be recreated. If the &quot;Selected Features&quot; list already contains any entries at this point, they will still be connected to items from the old model. This means editing the values will have no effect on the JSON view.</thetext>
          </long_desc>
          <long_desc isprivate="0">
            <commentid>25976</commentid>
            <who name="Daniel Wagner">daniel.wagner</who>
            <bug_when>2011-07-12 17:12:03 +0200</bug_when>
            <thetext>I can&#39;t find a quick fix for this in time for the 1.5 release. Deleting the Selected Features entries if the toggle is used caused more problems than it solved so I temporarily disabled the toggle feature (with r28149) until I can come up with a real fix.</thetext>
          </long_desc>
          <long_desc isprivate="0">
